examples.en: His wife was greedy for jewels.

examples.en: She wore her best jewels to the ball.

examples.en: I didn't steal these jewels, they've been planted on me.

examples.en: The black cloth sets off the jewels nicely.

examples.en: Some of these jewels have been smuggled in.

examples.en: Jewels look best seen against a dark background.

examples.en: She is spurning with her feet a casket of jewels.

examples.en: Someone got in and walked off with the jewels while we were out.
